	abstract = {In order to stress the importance of the visual communication design teaching for the industrial design major, and to satisfy the market demand of the visual elements of products, this thesis proposes the discussion of visual communication design aiming at the students in science and engineering. In the discussion, industrial design and the visual communication design will be re-interpreted vividly through students’ cases. The thesis tries to realize the teaching style which suits both the refined and popular tastes on the basis of the art effect of the “non-automatic design”, display of teaching achievement, the relationship between industrial design and the “non-automatic design” and so on. Through deep analysis of the visual communication design teaching for the industrial design major, the thesis tries to acknowledge the fact that the visual communication design is an important part of the industrial design major in regular college course. The contents and forms of the visual communication design course both develop and change with times. Meanwhile, the concept in teaching the “non-automatic design” tends to be more mature in the process of teaching of students majoring in industrial design. Undoubtedly, it will be one of the forward-looking fields of popular culture. © Sila Science. All Rights Reserved.},
